Package: scidigitizeR
Type: Package
Title: Standardized Medical Chart Reconstruction Engine
Version: 0.1.0
Author: SciDigitize AI Team
Maintainer: SciDigitize AI <support@scidigitize.ai>
Description: A configuration-driven plotting engine for reconstructing medical and 
